{"tid":2240712,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐，意大利套餐","createTime":"2020-10-13T00:38:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T12:06:59.000Z","uid":93141,"like":35,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"46965e3d762738d18f86b38588805e10d65539e2","tid":2240712,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T00:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5dDgq1M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5dDgq1M.jpg&h=6c52ccf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前菜 bruschetta: 麵包，番茄，ricotta，羅勒，蒜頭，胡椒，橄欖油<br />\n<br />\n蒜頭切開響麵包上用力摩擦，加橄欖油入焗爐焗到脆<br />\n加上ricotta，番茄，再稍為入焗爐加熱<br />\n最後加羅勒，胡椒粉，同橄欖油點綴<br />\n<br />\n主菜一 番茄羅勒意粉：意粉，番茄一開四，蒜頭切片，辣椒切碎，羅勒，橄欖油，白酒，胡椒，鹽，parmesan<br />\n<br />\npan中火落橄欖油，炒香蒜片同辣椒<br />\n蒜頭出水後落番茄，白酒，胡椒，鹽<br />\n白酒滾後落羅勒，加蓋煮兩分鐘<br />\n加al dente既意粉同少少意粉水，收汁後上碟<br />\n上碟後加羅勒，胡椒，parmesan，橄欖油點綴就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n主菜二 甜椒炆雞：雞腿(有冇骨都得)，紅蔥頭切碎，紅黃椒切塊，長辣椒對半切，迷迭香，蒜頭去皮，白酒，胡椒，鹽<br />\n<br />\n胡椒，鹽醃雞肉，中火煎到雞肉表面金黃，攞起備用<br />\n同煲大火爆香紅蔥頭，蒜頭，辣椒<br />\n開始乾時落紅黃椒，迷迭香翻炒，出香味後落白酒沖走煲底梅納反應物<br />\n白酒滾後落胡椒，鹽，撈勻<br />\n響材料最上擺返雞肉，加蓋轉細火煮25-30分鐘<br />\n攞起雞肉同甜椒擺碟，再用大火收汁，過篩後淋返上雞肉就搞掂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇落材料好似好多，其實大部分都係廚房常備野<br />\n而且三樣材料重疊唔少，可以一齊prep料，計好時間可以一齊煮好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n方法又簡單，好推薦大家輕鬆做好一個意大利大餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6ae6c4720922d9843cecef9bfe3f69422e5943","tid":2240712,"uid":5065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T00:39:57.000Z","msg":"得一君如愛，夫復何求<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f991e9ff40f17d8938b66f45b3a169fc1594427e","tid":2240712,"uid":93141,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T00:40:39.000Z","msg":"rare image of 樓豬響lab打食譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gQ62mBu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgQ62mBu.png&h=aef02d57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a44c3194e93a0ccfeabbbbe7fa0441171a4b0fc","tid":2240712,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c6ae6c4720922d9843cecef9bfe3f69422e5943","tid":2240712,"uid":5065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T00:39:57.000Z","msg":"得一君如愛，夫復何求<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T00:41:04.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165f22c81a913d419d6aa3b216aafc14250a4ca0","tid":2240712,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T00:42:50.000Z","msg":"打風我都想煮下lunch"},{"pid":"7d990c3d600d96e495097491e63a4542ad171857","tid":2240712,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"165f22c81a913d419d6aa3b216aafc14250a4ca0","tid":2240712,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T00:42:50.000Z","msg":"打風我都想煮下lunch"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T00:44:12.000Z","msg":"去啦，出面打住風，響屋企安心煮飯好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70caa96a3a8d1aa8d21c26dd02a7691aff899fdc","tid":2240712,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d990c3d600d96e495097491e63a4542ad171857","tid":2240712,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"165f22c81a913d419d6aa3b216aafc14250a4ca0","tid":2240712,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-